@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.63) - (v2 + 0.12 - v1 + 0.26)) / 0.78)
    v2 = 0.18
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.80)))
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.94 - v2 + 0.04) - v0) - wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.14)))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = (wp.sin(v0) * ((v0 + 0.22 + v2 + 0.40) * (v1 + 0.68 + v0 + 0.17)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
